# color object foregr backg option
#---------------------------------

# GENERAL config
## error message. Cursor line. Status bar. Tilde.
    color error color181 color236
    color indicator color231 color241
    color status color110 color236
    color tilde	color231 default

# INDEX config
## Default colors
    color index color231  color236 '.*'
## New messages. Replied messages. Deleted messages. Messages in a thread.
    color index color108 color236 ~N
    color index color140 color236 ~Q
    color index	color181 color236 ~D
    color index	color110 color236 ~v

# PAGER config 
## Header Colors
### default header colors
    color hdrdefault color108 color236
### subject color. Attachment color
    color header color140 color236 ^Subject:.*
    color attachment color110 color236
## Body Colors
### Mail addresses. Urls. Quotation. Signature.
    color body color110	default [\-\.+_a-zA-Z0-9]+@[\-\.a-zA-Z0-9]+
    color body color110	default	(https?|ftp)://[\-\.,/%~_:?&=\#a-zA-Z0-9]+
    color quoted color181 default
## Footer Colors
### signature color
    color signature  color212 default

